    <node id="&quot;EBENEZER SCROOGE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Ebenezer Scrooge is a young man in this passage, reflecting on his past as an apprentice under Fezziwig, showing nostalgia and affection for those times."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ebenezer Scrooge is the main character of 'A Christmas Carol,' a grasping, covetous old man who undergoes a transformation."&lt;SEP&gt;"The protagonist of the story, a miserly and skeptical man who is visited by ghosts that challenge his worldview."&lt;SEP&gt;"The protagonist of the story, a miserly businessman who is visited by spirits to change his ways."</data>
