    <node id="&quot;MRS. CRATCHIT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob Cratchit's wife in 'A Christmas Carol.'"&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob Cratchit's wife, who is industrious and caring, working diligently to support her family despite their hardships."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob Cratchit's wife, who prepares the family's Christmas dinner with the help of her children."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob's wife who shows affection towards him and their family."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob's wife, who openly expresses her dislike for Scrooge during their Christmas dinner."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob's wife, who prepares the Christmas dinner and takes pride in the pudding she made."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is the mother of the Cratchit family, who is affectionate and manages the household during Christmas celebrations."</data>
