    <node id="&quot;JACOB MARLEY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Jacob Marley is a deceased character mentioned in Scrooge's reflections, associated with the sexton's spade."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob Marley is a deceased character whose prediction Scrooge remembers, indicating his influence on Scrooge."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob Marley is a spirit who influenced Scrooge, mentioned in his reflections and gratitude."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob Marley is mentioned as the one who intervenes to send messengers to Scrooge."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob Marley is mentioned by Scrooge as he praises the Christmas Time for his transformation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob Marley is the ghost of Scrooge's former business partner who appears to warn Scrooge about the consequences of his actions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob Marley is the ghost of Scrooge's former business partner who appears to warn Scrooge about the consequences of his selfish and uncharitable life."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob Marley is the ghost of Scrooge's former business partner who warns Scrooge about his fate and the visits of Three Spirits."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-43c9bee23adfa77aa9dedd22401bba7d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91572b3cd42786ba4cb2f180ca25cbf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90b95db5c53e4364a6bee36b7aa4d70f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb661c37436355ccec2769b1d0350c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da2472b4ef2a535b62908f14d0fb0ca9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-359187e7571bda4b0b08b2e0b6581e52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-02baee20cc9463dbe08170a8e1043e32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1aa50206d02ed89418f65f97c6441d1c</data>
