    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CHAIN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Chain is a symbolic burden carried by Marley's Ghost, made of cash-boxes, keys, and other symbols of greed and earthly attachments."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Chain symbolizes the burdens and consequences of Jacob Marley's selfish life, which he forged link by link through his actions."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-359187e7571bda4b0b08b2e0b6581e52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1aa50206d02ed89418f65f97c6441d1c</data>
