    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE GHOST&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A supernatural figure whose province is the Future, guiding Scrooge."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost is a supernatural being that guides Scrooge through various visions and teaches him moral lessons."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost is a supernatural entity guiding Scrooge through visions of the past, present, and future, influencing his transformation."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost is a supernatural entity interacting with Scrooge, showing him shadows of the past."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost is a supernatural entity that forces Scrooge to observe scenes from his past, influencing his emotional state."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost is a supernatural entity that guides Scrooge through his past, revealing key moments that shaped his life."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost is a supernatural entity that reveals potential future events to Scrooge, including Tiny Tim's possible death."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost is the apparition of Jacob Marley who visits Scrooge to deliver a message about the importance of charity and the consequences of a life devoid of kindness."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost of Christmas Past is a supernatural entity that guides Scrooge through his past, showing him key moments that shaped his life."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost rebukes Scrooge and accompanies him through the streets, observing Christmas celebrations."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-19d72c57ae3408758b18d2568e86dc6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1a4fbcf1ed86864b9bfd5e8dba4c683&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54bdd22db1f84a965b5f4c06c9216d8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7637ff18c5ded77a68cce0a87883fad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-503f0bfa5453467c7c61d160a3540eca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da2472b4ef2a535b62908f14d0fb0ca9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ac129dc9b56f84c46760d153d68e93&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-359187e7571bda4b0b08b2e0b6581e52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
