    <node id="&quot;THE PHANTOM&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A supernatural being that reveals scenes to Scrooge, guiding his emotional journey."&lt;SEP&gt;"Another name for the Ghost of Christmas Yet to Come, a silent and ominous figure."&lt;SEP&gt;"Another term for Marley's Ghost, the spectral visitor who warns Scrooge."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Phantom accompanies Scrooge to the shop, where they witness the interactions among the old man and the other visitors."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Phantom is a spectral figure that guides Scrooge, pointing towards the body of the deceased man, adding to the eerie atmosphere."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Phantom is another name for Jacob Marley's ghost, emphasizing his tormented state and role as a warning to Scrooge."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Phantom is another name for the Ghost of Christmas Yet to Come, who shows Scrooge visions of the future."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Phantom is another name for the Spirit, which stands beside Scrooge and observes keenly."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-60fc063c79fc0d4acc91a57e79de04dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91572b3cd42786ba4cb2f180ca25cbf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1a4fbcf1ed86864b9bfd5e8dba4c683&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1f29eeadc1d8ab46dc8a0bbd3c56b64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb661c37436355ccec2769b1d0350c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ac129dc9b56f84c46760d153d68e93&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-359187e7571bda4b0b08b2e0b6581e52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-02baee20cc9463dbe08170a8e1043e32</data>
