    <node id="&quot;朱重八&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"朱元璋的原名，农民出身，参军后因才能突出逐渐崭露头角。"&lt;SEP&gt;"朱重八 is a poor peasant who struggles to bury his parents and later becomes a monk, enduring hardship and humiliation."&lt;SEP&gt;"朱重八 is a young man who suffers immense personal loss due to natural disasters and government neglect, later becoming a key figure in the rebellion against the Yuan Dynasty."&lt;SEP&gt;"朱重八，即朱元璋，是明朝的开国皇帝。他出身贫寒，经历过乞讨生活，后来加入明教，逐渐成长为一位坚强的领袖。他的经历塑造了他的性格和信仰。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;黄河&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"黄河 is the Yellow River, which flooded in 1344, causing widespread devastation and displacement of people in Shandong and Henan provinces."&lt;SEP&gt;"黄河是中国的母亲河，元末因治理不善导致民怨，成为农民起义的导火索。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;淮河&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"淮河 is the Huai River, which experienced severe plague and drought, exacerbating the suffering of the local population."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;脱脱&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"脱脱 is a famous chancellor of the Yuan Dynasty, known for his reforms and清廉 (integrity), but his decision to repair the Yellow River inadvertently contributed to the dynasty's downfall."&lt;SEP&gt;"脱脱是元朝的大臣，主张治理黄河，但因官吏腐败导致民怨沸腾，加速了元朝的灭亡。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;元顺帝&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"元顺帝 is the emperor of the Yuan Dynasty during this period, whose government was corrupt and ineffective in addressing the disasters."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;刘德&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"刘德 is a landlord who refuses to help朱重八 bury his parents, showing a cold and indifferent attitude."&lt;SEP&gt;"刘德 is a landlord who refuses to help朱重八 bury his parents, symbolizing the indifference of the wealthy towards the suffering of the poor."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;黄河泛滥&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"黄河泛滥 refers to the flooding of the Yellow River in 1344, which displaced hundreds of thousands and became a catalyst for rebellion."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
