      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"淮河沿岸瘟疫和旱灾 refers to the plague and drought along the Huai River, which caused further suffering and death among the population."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;石人一只眼，挑动黄河天下反&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"石人一只眼，挑动黄河天下反 is a prophetic statement indicating the coming rebellion against the Yuan Dynasty, triggered by the Yellow River flooding."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;山东&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"山东 is a province in China heavily affected by the Yellow River flooding, leading to widespread displacement and suffering."&lt;SEP&gt;"民工在山东境内挖出独眼石人，成为起义的直接导火索。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;河南&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"河南 is a province in China that, along with Shandong, suffered greatly from the Yellow River flooding in 1344."&lt;SEP&gt;"河南 is another region where朱重八 is sent to beg for food, further shaping his resilience and understanding of the world."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;中书省&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"中书省 is the central administrative body of the Yuan Dynasty, responsible for handling government affairs, including disaster relief."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;元代&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"元代 refers to the Yuan Dynasty period when monks could marry and own property, contextualizing朱重八's experiences."&lt;SEP&gt;"元代 refers to the Yuan Dynasty's administrative system, which was characterized by corruption and inefficiency during this period."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;尧舜禹汤&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"尧舜禹汤 are legendary sage kings of Chinese antiquity, used here as flattering comparisons for the emperor by corrupt officials."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;地主&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"地主 refers to the landlord class during the Yuan Dynasty, who often exploited peasants like Zhu Chongba's family."&lt;SEP&gt;"地主 represents the landlord class who own land but do not labor, contrasting sharply with朱重八's impoverished family."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;倒插门&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"倒插门 refers to the practice of uxorilocal marriage where Zhu Chongba's third brother went to live with his wife's family."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;赈灾&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"赈灾 refers to the disaster relief efforts that were corrupted at every level of the Yuan government, leaving little aid for actual victims."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;朱元璋&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"朱元璋 is the later name of朱重八, who recalls the emotional pain of his early life after achieving stability."&lt;SEP&gt;"朱元璋原名朱重八，是明朝的开国皇帝。他在军队中表现出色，作战勇敢，有计谋，处事冷静，思虑深远，讲义气，有威信。他自学过一些字，分析问题准确，逐渐成为郭子兴的智囊。他将名字改为朱元璋，意为诛灭元朝的利器。"&lt;SEP&gt;"朱元璋是朱重八的正式姓名，明朝的开国皇帝，从贫苦农民成长为一代帝王，经历了乞讨、起义到建立政权的全过程。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;皇觉寺&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"皇觉寺 is a temple where朱重八 becomes a monk, but the monks there treat him poorly and exploit his labor."&lt;SEP&gt;"皇觉寺是朱重八早年出家为僧的寺庙，也是他乞讨生活后回归的地方。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;淮西&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"淮西 is a region where朱重八 is sent to beg for food during a famine, and where he gains valuable life experiences."&lt;SEP&gt;"淮西是朱重八乞讨生活的地方，他在那里度过了三年，经历了人生的重大转变。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;饥荒&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"饥荒 is a severe famine that forces朱重八 and others to beg for food, marking a turning point in his life."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;化缘&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"化缘 is the practice of begging for food, which朱重八 is forced into during the famine, exposing him to further hardship."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;朱重八的二哥&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"朱重八的二哥 helps朱重八 carry their parents' bodies in search of a burial place, showing familial solidarity in hardship."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;好心人&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"好心人 is an unnamed benefactor who pities朱重八 and provides land to bury his parents."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;太上老君&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"太上老君 is a Taoist deity whom朱重八 prays to during his desperate times."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;如来佛祖&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"如来佛祖 is a Buddhist figure朱重八 appeals to for help during his suffering."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;弥勒佛&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"弥勒佛 is the future Buddha of明教, whom朱重八 comes to believe will bring salvation during dark times."&lt;SEP&gt;"弥勒佛是佛教中的未来佛，朱重八信仰弥勒佛，认为他会在黑暗时代降世拯救世人。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;唐僧&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"唐僧 is referenced humorously as a comparison to the practice of化缘 (begging for food)."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;明教&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"明教 is a religious sect朱重八 adopts, believing in the coming of弥勒佛 during times of darkness."&lt;SEP&gt;"明教是一个宗教组织，朱重八曾信仰明教，相信弥勒佛会降世拯救世人。明教在元末农民起义中扮演了重要角色。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;颖州&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"颖州（今安徽阜阳）是韩山童和刘福通起义的地方，也是朱重八曾经乞讨过的地方。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;韩山童&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"韩山童是元末农民起义的领袖之一，自称宋朝皇室后裔，与刘福通一起发动起义。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;刘福通&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"刘福通是元末农民起义的领袖之一，自称刘光世大将的后人，与韩山童一起发动起义。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;白莲教&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"白莲教是元末农民起义中使用的宗教组织，韩山童和刘福通利用白莲教发动起义。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;元朝&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The ruling dynasty that oppressed peasants with heavy taxes and corvée labor, leading to widespread rebellion."&lt;SEP&gt;"元朝是蒙古人建立的王朝，末期腐败严重，导致农民起义频发，最终灭亡。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;石人一只眼&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"石人一只眼是元末农民起义中的象征性事件，民工挖出独眼石人，背部刻有‘挑动黄河天下反’的字样，引发起义。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;陈胜吴广&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"陈胜吴广是秦末农民起义的领袖，文中作为历史类比提到，象征农民起义领袖的宿命。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;宋朝&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"宋朝是被元朝灭亡的前朝，韩山童自称宋朝皇室后裔以增强起义合法性。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;刘光世&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"南宋抗金名将，刘福通伪托为其后人以提升号召力。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;至正十一年&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"元朝年号（1351年），黄河工程引发大规模起义的关键时间节点。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;徭役&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"元朝官吏借修河堤之名强征民夫，成为压迫百姓的重要手段。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;宿命&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"文中指农民起义领袖往往先起义后失败的历史循环规律。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;千户&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ROLE"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A military rank in the rebel army, held by someone who invited Zhu Chongba (Zhu Yuanzhang) to join."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;寺庙&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"LOCATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The temple where Zhu Chongba initially sought refuge to survive, before being forced to join the rebellion."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;封建时代&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The feudal era in which peasants had no choice but to rebel due to extreme oppression."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;算卦&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The divination performed by Zhou Dexing to advise Zhu Chongba on whether to flee, stay, or rebel."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;告发&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The act of someone reporting Zhu Chongba for reading the rebel letter, forcing him into rebellion."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;至正十二年&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The year 1352, when Zhu Chongba joined Guo Zixing's rebel forces in Haozhou."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;月牙铲&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A metaphorical description of Zhu Yuanzhang's distinctive facial features (protruding forehead and chin)."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;郭子兴&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"郭子兴是朱元璋的早期领导，地主出身，性情暴躁，不能容人。他起初信任朱元璋，但后来因嫉妒朱元璋的能力而疏远甚至迫害他。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;汤和&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"汤和是朱元璋的同乡，在军队中官职较高但尊敬朱元璋。他识实务，有远见，后来在腥风血雨中幸存下来。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;马姑娘&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"马姑娘是郭子兴的义女，朱元璋的妻子，对朱元璋的成功起到关键作用。她给朱元璋带来了家庭的温暖和支持。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;孙德崖&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"孙德崖是濠州的农民起义军统帅之一，与郭子兴有深刻矛盾。他参与绑架郭子兴，后被朱元璋揭露贪污公款的行为。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;濠州&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"濠州是朱元璋和郭子兴等人活动的地区，是起义军的重要据点。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;起义军&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"起义军是由郭子兴、朱元璋等人领导的反对元朝的军事组织。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;绑架郭子兴事件&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"郭子兴被孙德崖等人绑架并殴打，朱元璋成功救出他。这一事件让朱元璋意识到跟随这些人没有前途。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;九人长&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ROLE"</data>
      <data key="d1">"朱元璋的第一个官职，在参军两个月后因才能被提拔。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;总管&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ROLE"</data>
      <data key="d1">"朱元璋在起义军中担任的职位，负责财务和管理，严于律己。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;郭子兴的儿子&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"郭子兴之子，对朱元璋落井下石，曾吩咐守兵不给朱元璋送饭。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;孙德崖等四人&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"濠州农民起义军的四位统帅，与地主出身的郭子兴存在深刻矛盾。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;贪污公款事件&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"孙德崖等人贪污公款被朱元璋掌握证据，成为救郭子兴的筹码。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;朱元璋被囚禁事件&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"郭子兴因嫉妒将朱元璋关押，其子甚至断其饮食。"</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;周德兴&quot;">
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d1">"周德兴为朱重八提供算卦的建议，帮助他决定是否参加起义。"</data>
      <data key="d0">"UNKNOWN"</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;濠州城&quot;">
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d1">"朱重八在濠州城投军并开始他的军事生涯。"</data>
      <data key="d0">"UNKNOWN"</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;逼上梁山&quot;">
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d1">"朱重八被逼无奈参加起义军，象征贫苦农民的反抗。"</data>
      <data key="d0">"UNKNOWN"</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;农民起义&quot;">
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d1">"朱重八是农民起义的代表人物，领导起义军推翻元朝统治。"</data>
      <data key="d0">"UNKNOWN"</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;元军&quot;">
      <data key="d2">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d1">"起义军与元军是敌对关系，双方在濠州城等地展开战斗。"</data>
      <data key="d0">"UNKNOWN"</data>
    </node>
