      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Project Gutenberg offers 'A Christmas Carol' as a free eBook."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;PROJECT GUTENBERG&quot;" target="&quot;PROJECT GUTENBERG LITERARY ARCHIVE FOUNDATION&quot;">
      <data key="d4">27.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"The Foundation manages and supports Project Gutenberg, ensuring its mission of free distribution of electronic works."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Project Gutenberg Literary Archive Foundation manages the Project Gutenberg trademark and receives royalties related to Project Gutenberg works."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Project Gutenberg Literary Archive Foundation supports and manages the Project Gutenberg mission and its electronic works."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-85f77f5e3a9aba01133555a2d20e2fd8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-194cd9680f4967f48bea89678f7ece21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af4ae173c561e4594c5aea96198cce9d</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
