      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;刘德&quot;">
      <data key="d4">14.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"刘德's refusal to help朱重八 bury his parents symbolizes the societal indifference that fuels朱重八's later rebellion."&lt;SEP&gt;"朱重八 seeks help from刘德 to bury his parents, but刘德 refuses, highlighting the harsh social hierarchy."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
