    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;地主&quot;">
      <data key="d4">16.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"The landlord class, represented by Liu De, oppressed peasants like Zhu Chongba and his family."&lt;SEP&gt;"地主 symbolizes the oppressive system朱重八 resents, fueling his later rebellion."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
