      <data key="d4">6.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Zhu Chongba's third brother's uxorilocal marriage left fewer family members to help during the crisis."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;皇觉寺&quot;">
      <data key="d4">14.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱重八 joins皇觉寺 as a monk but is exploited and mistreated by the monks there."&lt;SEP&gt;"朱重八早年出家为僧的寺庙，也是他乞讨生活后回归的地方，对他的成长有重要影响。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
