      <data key="d4">17.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱重八 is sent to淮西 to beg for food, where he gains critical life experiences and insights."&lt;SEP&gt;"朱重八在淮西乞讨三年，经历了人生的重大转变，从无助的孩童成长为坚强的战士。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
