      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"化缘 is the activity朱重八 is forced into during the famine, exposing him to humiliation and survival challenges."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;朱元璋&quot;">
      <data key="d4">29.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋 is the later identity of朱重八, reflecting on his past struggles after achieving success."&lt;SEP&gt;"朱元璋是朱重八称帝后的正式姓名，同一人物的不同阶段称谓。"&lt;SEP&gt;"朱重八是朱元璋的原名，后改名为朱元璋以表明反元志向。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
