    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;汤和&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"汤和是朱重八的第一个战友，陪同他参加起义军并成为他的重要支持者。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;郭子兴&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"郭子兴最初怀疑朱重八是奸细，后因他的才能将他留在身边作为亲兵。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;起义军&quot;">
      <data key="d4">10.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱重八最终加入并领导了起义军，成为其核心人物。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;濠州城&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱重八在濠州城投军并开始他的军事生涯。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;逼上梁山&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱重八被逼无奈参加起义军，象征贫苦农民的反抗。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;农民起义&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱重八是农民起义的代表人物，领导起义军推翻元朝统治。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;千户&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Zhu Chongba was invited by a 'qianhu' (commander) to join the rebellion, but initially hesitated."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;寺庙&quot;">
      <data key="d4">6.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Zhu Chongba initially hid in a temple to avoid starvation before being forced into rebellion."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;元朝&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Zhu Chongba rebelled against the Yuan Dynasty due to its oppressive policies."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;封建时代&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Zhu Chongba's rebellion was a product of the extreme oppression of the feudal era."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;算卦&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Zhou Dexing advised Zhu Chongba through divination, pushing him toward rebellion."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;告发&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Zhu Chongba was forced into rebellion after someone reported him for reading the rebel letter."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱重八&quot;" target="&quot;至正十二年&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Zhu Chongba officially joined Guo Zixing's rebellion in 1352."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;黄河&quot;" target="&quot;脱脱&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"脱脱主张治理黄河，但因官吏腐败导致民怨沸腾，加速了元朝的灭亡。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;黄河&quot;" target="&quot;石人一只眼&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"黄河治理工程中挖出独眼石人，引发民工起义，成为元末农民起义的导火索。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;黄河&quot;" target="&quot;至正十一年&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"该年元朝启动黄河治理工程，成为大起义的导火索。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;脱脱&quot;" target="&quot;黄河泛滥&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"脱脱's decision to repair the Yellow River inadvertently sets the stage for the rebellion against the Yuan Dynasty."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;脱脱&quot;" target="&quot;至正十一年&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"脱脱在该年主导治河工程决策。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;元顺帝&quot;" target="&quot;淮河沿岸瘟疫和旱灾&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"元顺帝's government fails to effectively address the plague and drought along the Huai River, exacerbating the suffering of the people."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;元顺帝&quot;" target="&quot;尧舜禹汤&quot;">
      <data key="d4">5.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Corrupt officials flattered the emperor by comparing him to legendary sage kings, despite his government's failures."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;黄河泛滥&quot;" target="&quot;淮河沿岸瘟疫和旱灾&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Both the Yellow River flooding and the Huai River plague/drought are natural disasters that contribute to the suffering and unrest during the Yuan Dynasty."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;黄河泛滥&quot;" target="&quot;石人一只眼，挑动黄河天下反&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"The prophetic statement foreshadows the rebellion triggered by the Yellow River flooding."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;黄河泛滥&quot;" target="&quot;山东&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Shandong province was one of the main areas devastated by the Yellow River flooding in 1344."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;黄河泛滥&quot;" target="&quot;河南&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"Henan province was severely impacted by the Yellow River flooding, creating numerous refugees."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;山东&quot;" target="&quot;石人一只眼&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"独眼石人在山东境内被挖出，触发起义。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;中书省&quot;" target="&quot;赈灾&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"The中书省 was responsible for organizing disaster relief, but corruption meant little aid reached the people."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;中书省&quot;" target="&quot;元代&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"中书省 was the central governing body of the Yuan Dynasty's administrative system."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90074c0167f1b96f110e0701bbd3370b</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;元代&quot;" target="&quot;皇觉寺&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"皇觉寺's lax monastic practices reflect the broader societal norms of the元代 period."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-b26706fdda696524be1e5ff48c2836c2</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;元朝&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋最终推翻元朝建立明朝。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;郭子兴&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋最初是郭子兴的亲兵长和智囊，但后来郭子兴因嫉妒朱元璋的能力而疏远和迫害他。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;汤和&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"汤和是朱元璋的同乡和早期支持者，尊敬朱元璋并帮助他在军队中晋升。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;马姑娘&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"马姑娘是朱元璋的妻子，给他带来了家庭的温暖和支持，是他成功的关键因素之一。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;孙德崖&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋揭露孙德崖的贪污行为并救出被绑架的郭子兴，展现了朱元璋的智慧和勇气。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;濠州&quot;">
      <data key="d4">6.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋在濠州活动，参与起义军并逐渐崛起。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;起义军&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋是起义军的重要成员，逐渐成为其核心领导者。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;绑架郭子兴事件&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋在绑架郭子兴事件中表现出色，救出郭子兴并揭露孙德崖的恶行。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;九人长&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋因才能被提拔为九人长，是其军事生涯的第一个官职。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;总管&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋担任起义军总管，严于律己，管理财务事务。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;朱元璋&quot;" target="&quot;贪污公款事件&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"朱元璋利用掌握的贪污证据迫使孙德崖释放郭子兴。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;韩山童&quot;" target="&quot;刘福通&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"韩山童和刘福通是元末农民起义的领袖，共同发动起义，利用白莲教组织群众。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;韩山童&quot;" target="&quot;白莲教&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"韩山童利用白莲教组织起义，自称宋朝皇室后裔，增强起义的合法性。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;韩山童&quot;" target="&quot;宋朝&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"韩山童伪称宋朝皇室后裔以获取民众支持。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;刘福通&quot;" target="&quot;白莲教&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"刘福通与韩山童一起利用白莲教组织起义，自称刘光世大将的后人。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;刘福通&quot;" target="&quot;刘光世&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"刘福通伪托为南宋名将刘光世后人以增强威信。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;元朝&quot;" target="&quot;徭役&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"元朝官吏通过强征徭役加剧社会矛盾。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;元朝&quot;" target="&quot;封建时代&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"The Yuan Dynasty was part of the oppressive feudal system that provoked peasant revolts."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;陈胜吴广&quot;" target="&quot;宿命&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"作为历史先例象征农民领袖'首义必败'的规律。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9a76d8ffa3427c606f749054f4201706</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;封建时代&quot;" target="&quot;起义军&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"The rebel army emerged as a response to the unbearable conditions of the feudal era."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;至正十二年&quot;" target="&quot;郭子兴&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"In 1352, Guo Zixing was leading the rebel defense of Haozhou against the Yuan army."</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;郭子兴&quot;" target="&quot;起义军&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"郭子兴是濠州城起义军的领袖，朱重八最初投奔他的部队。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;郭子兴&quot;" target="&quot;濠州城&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"郭子兴在濠州城领导起义军抵抗元军的围困。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-ae09d8cc60b0994e2115ddece8322649</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;郭子兴&quot;" target="&quot;孙德崖&quot;">
      <data key="d4">7.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"郭子兴和孙德崖是起义军中的对立派系，矛盾深刻，最终导致郭子兴被绑架。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;郭子兴&quot;" target="&quot;郭子兴的儿子&quot;">
      <data key="d4">6.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"郭子兴之子参与迫害朱元璋，反映内部权力斗争。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;郭子兴&quot;" target="&quot;朱元璋被囚禁事件&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"郭子兴因猜忌囚禁朱元璋，导致关系彻底恶化。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;孙德崖&quot;" target="&quot;孙德崖等四人&quot;">
      <data key="d4">8.0</data>
      <data key="d5">"孙德崖是四人集团首领，共同对抗郭子兴势力。"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-4bdd775f30019125ecf386a970f73cb9</data>
      <data key="d7">1</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;起义军&quot;" target="&quot;元军&quot;">
      <data key="d4">9.0</data>
